title: 151: Chargers to LA, coaching hires, Divisional round upsets?
itunes:title: 151: Chargers to LA, coaching hires, Divisional round upsets?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss the latest NFL news with the Chargers moving to Los Angeles and the NFL coaching seats filling up in Buffalo, Denver and Jacksonville. The duo also preview the NFL Divisional Playoffs and break down what teams have the best chance of pulling an upset. Also, listen for the best running back to come out of the 2017 NFL Draft class.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
